Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:54.17,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Reality slips far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:56.13,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Fiction comes alive, we start to play it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:57.80,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Hope is no more, behind a closed door
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.68,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}As we drift away from where we were before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.64,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Hope and hopelessness become one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.64,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}It's all meaningless, we've already begun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:05.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Yup, we are all one and the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Never opposites, we play the same game
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:09.35,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Walk the thin line between hope and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:11.19,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Running from the truth, but it's already here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.11,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Told so many lies, I dunno if they can find me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:14.99,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Only one life to live, so choose wisely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:16.86,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Heads or tails, do you even know the side you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:18.74,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Doesn't really matter if it's on the same coin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.53,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}If you wanna achieve you gotta believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:22.20,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}It's on right now, there's the door here's the key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:26.12,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\t(350,510,\c&HD1CDDB&\3aff\4aff)}The search is so very long, we let it fade away
